Definition: a nerve cell whose body is outside the central nervous system
Example: damage to ganglion cells in the retina may play a role in the development of glaucoma
Synonyms: gangliocyte, nerve_cell, a, nerve, cell, whose, body, is, outside, the, central, nervous, system, damage, to, ganglion, cells, in, retina, may, play, role, development, of, glaucoma
Category: noun.body
